---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 space-y-6">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span>ðŸš€</span> Welcome to MaiPDF!
  </h1>

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    MaiPDF is a powerful platform that enables secure and customizable PDF sharing.
    With MaiPDF, users can easily upload, share, and control access to PDF documents
    with features like customizable access limits, download restrictions, and email verification.
  </p>

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    Whether you're looking to share confidential reports, invoices, or any other type of document,
    MaiPDF provides an intuitive and secure solution for document sharing.
    The platform gives you full control over who can view and download your files,
    making it the ideal choice for sensitive information.
  </p>

  <div>
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Key features of MaiPDF include:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-base leading-relaxed">
      <li><strong>Secure PDF Sharing:</strong> Share PDF files with a unique, secure link.</li>
      <li><strong>Customizable Access Limits:</strong> Set expiration dates or restrict access by IP address or user email.</li>
      <li><strong>Download Restrictions:</strong> Control whether users can download the document or only view it.</li>
      <li><strong>Email Verification:</strong> Ensure that only authorized users can access your PDFs with email verification before viewing the document.</li>
      <li><strong>Customizable Permissions:</strong> Manage permissions such as read-only or edit access for specific users or groups.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    MaiPDF is perfect for businesses, educators, or anyone needing a reliable and secure solution
    for sharing important PDF files while maintaining full control over the distribution and access to those files.
  </p>

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    To get started, simply upload your PDF files, customize your sharing settings,
    and share the secure link with your recipients. It's that simple!
  </p>

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
    For more information or to start using MaiPDF, visit our 
    <a href="https://maipdf.com" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-600 ml-1">MaiPDF website</a>.
  </p>
</main>

<script>
  window.toggleTheme = () => {
    const htmlElement = document.documentElement;
    const isDarkMode = htmlElement.classList.contains('dark');
    if (isDarkMode) {
      htmlElement.classList.remove('dark');
      localStorage.setItem('theme', 'light');
    } else {
      htmlElement.classList.add('dark');
      localStorage.setItem('theme', 'dark');
    }
  };

  // Set theme on page load
  const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
  if (savedTheme === 'dark') {
    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
  }
</script>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
